'''兩西西里足球代表隊'''是意大利南部[[兩西西里王國|兩西西里王國]]地區的一個足球代表隊。該球隊並不是FIFA和UEFA的會員，因此無法參加世界杯和歐錦賽的賽事。兩西西里組建於2008年<ref>{{cite web |last= Marseglia |first= Cosimo Enrico |url= http://www.corrieresalentino.it/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=870:e-nata-la-nazionale-di-calcio-del-regno-delle-due-sicilie&catid=37:sport&Itemid=68 |title= È nata la Nazionale di Calcio del Regno delle Due Sicilie |accessdate= February 1, 2014 |publisher= Corrieresalentino.it |date= January 28, 2009 |archive-date= 2016-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205832/http://www.corrieresalentino.it/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=870:e-nata-la-nazionale-di-calcio-del-regno-delle-due-sicilie&catid=37:sport&Itemid=68 }}{{it icon}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Marro |first=Fiore |url=http://comitatiduesicilie.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1246 |title=Presentazione della Nazionale di Calcio del Regno delle Due Sicilie |accessdate=February 1, 2014 |publisher=Comitati Due Sicilie |date=December 16, 2008 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725185806/http://comitatiduesicilie.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=1246 |archivedate=2011年7月25日 }}{{it icon}}</ref>。2009年4月30日，兩西西里和[[帕達尼亞足球代表隊|帕達尼亞足球代表隊]]進行了一場比賽，這是他們的首場比賽<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.duesicilie.org/spip.php?article54 |title= Positivo esordio della Nazionale delle Due Sicilie |accessdate= February 1, 2014 |publisher= Associazione Culturale Due Sicilie - Duesicilie.org |date= May 3, 2009 |archive-date= 2016-03-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170647/http://www.duesicilie.org/spip.php?article54 |dead-url= no }}{{it icon}}</ref>。兩西西里在2010年1月成為[[新足球聯盟理事會|新足球聯盟理事會]]的暫定會員<ref>[http://www.nf-board.com/cp/cp27_en.pdf NF Board – Press release n.27] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nf-board.com/cp/cp27_en.pdf |date=20110714180947 }}{{en icon}}</ref>。並參加了這一年的萬歲世界杯。
